{
  "texts": [
    "Note that agents can be equipped with multiple tools, so scenarios may overlap for a specific case.",
    "In such cases, we assign the most relevant category to ensure proper classification.",
    "Safety issues of LLM agents are diverse.",
    "To cover as many circumstances as possible, we define 10 risk types according to research and related work including Safetybench and ToolEmu.",
    "Risk types are hard to define accurately."
  ]
}